CONTEXT.InputsProvided:
Subject description (required); style preference (optional, default:
minimalist); output width (optional, default: 80 characters max);
rendering context (optional, default: terminal display).

TREE_OF_THOUGHT.Depth:
1 level of sub-branching — compare top-level approaches only;
    do not recurse into sub-style variations unless the user requests
    multiple variants.

AdaptWhen.Condition:
Expand character density range to full spectrum (space through @);
increase row count (16–24 rows); apply multi-level shading gradients;
add internal structural features beyond the outline.

ConditionalLogic.Condition:
Prioritize facial features; increase vertical resolution to 20+ rows;
use wider aspect ratio; render eye spacing and facial structure first
before adding hair, beard, or hat.
